Her elder half-brother Hyacinth was Duke of Mead before her, but Hyacinth died without heirs.
Su hermanastro mayor Hyacinth era Duque de Mead antes que ella, pero Hyacinth murió sin herederos.
Before his death, Hyacinth was scandalously involved with Paulus, the old Duke of Ursul - Ignatius' father!
Antes de su muerte, Hyacinth estaba implicado escandalosamente con Paulus, el antiguo Duque de Ursul - El Padre Ignatius!
Hyacinth's death was under mysterious circumstances and may have been suicide or murder.
La muerte de Hyacinth ocurrió bajo extrañas circunstancias y pudo haber sido un suicidio o un asesinato.
Her brother Kevan lives with her.
